OL,3,CVirgin Media fined #23.8m for putting
OL,4,Cvulnerable customers at risk
OL,6,FOfcom has fined Virgin Media #23.8
OL,7,Fmillion after disconnecting vulnerable
OL,8,Fcustomers' alarms while moving them to
OL,9,Fdigital services.
OL,11,FSeveral serious incidents took place
OL,12,Fwhile Virgin was upgrading its
OL,13,Fcustomers' home phone services in
OL,14,FNovember and December 2023, the media
OL,15,Fand communications watchdog said.
