OL,3,CVirgin Media fined #23.8m for putting
OL,4,Cvulnerable customers at risk
OL,6,FVirgin failed to properly identify and
OL,7,Frecord the status of its "telecare"
OL,8,Fcustomers, who have emergency alarm
OL,9,Fsystems that connect to a monitoring
OL,10,Fservice ` meaning those affected did
OL,11,Fnot receive the right amount of
OL,12,Fsupport.
OL,14,FThis led to many of these alarm users
OL,15,Fhaving their systems disconnected. The
OL,16,Fwatchdog said this put thousands of
OL,17,Fvulnerable customers at direct risk of
OL,18,Fharm.
