OL,3,CVirgin Media fined #23.8m for putting
OL,4,Cvulnerable customers at risk
OL,6,FIan Strawhorne, Ofcom's director of
OL,7,Fenforcement, said: "It's unacceptable
OL,8,Fthat vulnerable customers were put at
OL,9,Fdirect risk of harm and left without
OL,10,Fappropriate support by Virgin Media
OL,11,Fduring what should have been a safe
OL,12,Fand straightforward upgrade to their
OL,13,Flandline services.
OL,15,F"Today's fine makes clear to companies
OL,16,Fthat if they fail to protect their
OL,17,Fvulnerable customers, they can expect
OL,18,Fto face similar enforcement action."
