OL,3,CVirgin Media fined #23.8m for putting
OL,4,Cvulnerable customers at risk
OL,6,FVirgin has four weeks to pay the fine,
OL,7,Fwhich will then be passed to the
OL,8,FTreasury.
OL,10,FThe penalty took into account the
OL,11,Fseriousness of the breach, and the
OL,12,Fvulnerability of the customers
OL,13,Faffected ` as well as the fact that
OL,14,FVirgin self-reported the incident and
OL,15,Fadmitted its failings.
