OL,3,CVirgin Media fined #23.8m for putting
OL,4,Cvulnerable customers at risk
OL,6,FA spokesman for Virgin said it had
OL,7,Fupdated its procedures since 2023 and
OL,8,Fintroduced further safeguards to
OL,9,Fimprove its treatment of vulnerable
OL,10,Fcustomers.
OL,12,F"While historically the majority of
OL,13,Fmigrations were completed without
OL,14,Fissue, we recognise that we didn't get
OL,15,Feverything right and have since
OL,16,Faddressed the migration issues
OL,17,Fidentified by Ofcom," the company said.
