OL,3,CVirgin Media fined #23.8m for putting
OL,4,Cvulnerable customers at risk
OL,6,FThis includes a package of support for
OL,7,Fvulnerable customers, including
OL,8,Fimproved communications, additional at-
OL,9,Fhome support, and extensive checks
OL,10,Ffollowing the switchover, as well as
OL,11,Ftaking part in a national awareness
OL,12,Fcampaign.
OL,14,FThe firm also stressed that it was
OL,15,F"essential we move our customers to
OL,16,Fdigital services" from traditional
OL,17,Fanalogue landlines, which are "less
OL,18,Freliable and difficult to maintain".
